<div id='ZimbraWikiPage'>
	<table class="zmwiki-chromeTable" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody>
	<tr><td class="zmwiki-headerContainer" colspan=2>
		<wiklet class='INLINE' page="_Header" inherit="true" />
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="zmwiki-sideBarContainer" valign="top" rowspan="2">
			<wiklet class='INLINE' page="_SideBar" inherit="true" />
		</td>

		<td class="zmwiki-titleBarContainer" valign="top">
			<wiklet class='INLINE' page="_VersionTitleBar" inherit="true" />
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="zmwiki-contentContainer" valign="top">
			<wiklet class='CONTENT' />
		</td>
	</tr>
	<!--tr><td class="zmwiki-footerContainer" colspan=2>
		<xwiklet class='INLINE' page="_Footer" inherit="true" />
	</td></tr-->
	</tbody></table>
</div>
